00:00:23.540 --> 00:00:28.960
This Swiss bank safe full of money is available
to be purchased and then moved and rebuilt

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.740
anywhere in the world.

00:00:30.740 --> 00:00:35.310
It's the original bank safe from the Schweizer
Volksbank built in the 1912.

00:00:35.310 --> 00:00:42.079
There are 1619 deposit boxes with original
keys and 8 million pieces of Swiss 5 cent

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:45.690
coins which is 15 tons of liquid money.

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:51.880
A 75 year old French man was given a revolutionary
heart transplant using a new artificial heart.

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:55.262
The Carmat artificial heart is expected to
operate for as long as five years and hopes

00:00:55.262 --> 00:01:00.460
to give the patient the ability to live a
normal life until a real heart can be donated.

00:01:00.460 --> 00:01:04.809
Unlike artificial hearts used in the past
it was developed to fully replicate the self-regulated

00:01:04.809 --> 00:01:10.200
contractions of a real heart by using an intricate
system of sensors and microprocessors that

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:14.450
monitors the body's internal changes and alters
the blood flow accordingly.

00:01:14.450 --> 00:01:18.990
Brothers Simon and Chris Parke are launching
their underwater jet pack.

00:01:18.990 --> 00:01:24.600
The arm worn propulsion system uses digital
motors and wireless controls to operate.

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:27.359
Giving people a new way to explore underwater.

00:01:27.359 --> 00:01:33.320
POE is an interactive urinal concept that
measures your pee... so yeah.

